<plot>Growing up isn't all it's cracked up to be. Just ask third-grader, Ella Johansen (played by Libby Adams), who just wants to be a kid.....forever. When third-grader, Ella Johansen's parents don't show up for Career Day, Ella's teacher pushes her to take the stage and explain how she sees her own career. Career Day is a satiric look at society through the eyes and imagination of a nine year old!</plot><url>http://localhost:8983/solr/movie.html?094251</url></doc>
